<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>string-width</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">&gt;<sp/>Get<sp/>the<sp/>visual<sp/>width<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>string<sp/>-<sp/>the<sp/>number<sp/>of<sp/>columns<sp/>required<sp/>to<sp/>display<sp/>it</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Some<sp/>Unicode<sp/>characters<sp/>are<sp/>[fullwidth](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Halfwidth_and_fullwidth_forms)<sp/>and<sp/>use<sp/>double<sp/>the<sp/>normal<sp/>width.<sp/>[ANSI<sp/>escape<sp/>codes](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ANSI_escape_code)<sp/>are<sp/>stripped<sp/>and<sp/>doesn&apos;t<sp/>affect<sp/>the<sp/>width.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Useful<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>able<sp/>to<sp/>measure<sp/>the<sp/>actual<sp/>width<sp/>of<sp/>command-line<sp/>output.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Install</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">$<sp/>npm<sp/>install<sp/>string-width</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Usage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```js</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">const<sp/>stringWidth<sp/>=<sp/>require(&apos;string-width&apos;);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">stringWidth(&apos;a&apos;);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//=&gt;<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">stringWidth(&apos;古&apos;);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//=&gt;<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">stringWidth(&apos;\u001B[1m古\u001B[22m&apos;);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//=&gt;<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
